<paragraph blockId="1.[173,1127,659,1142]" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
P-2 very enlarged, a large thin long projection in the anteroventral and a small projection in the distoventral P-1-5 L: 22(23)-108(110)-47(48)-104(106)-40(40) = 321, H: 29(29)- 97(98)-60(59)-30(30)-17(17) (
<figureCitation box="[467,536,861,883]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="3.[174,210,1488,1510]" captionTargetBox="[177,1125,780,1457]" captionTargetId="figure-199@3.[174,1126,776,1459]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Fig. 4. Kongsbergia ermani sp. n., male a) gnathosoma b) IV-L outside view c) IV-L inside view" figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5734799" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5734799/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
